Set Up Desk Phones for Your Contact Center

You can set up desk phones or headphones in your telephony system so that your agents can use them to answer and make calls.

This feature is available with Service Cloud Voice with Amazon Connect, Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect, and Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony.

To set up desk phones for the Amazon Connect telephony provider:

Log in to the AWS Management Console, click Services, and then click Amazon Connect.
Click the Amazon Connect instance that matches the name of your Service Cloud Voice contact center.
Click Users and then User management.
Select the users you want to grant desk phone access. Click Edit.
Select Desk phone as the Phone Type and enter the phone number.
Save your changes.

After setup, agents can select desk phone from the Omn-Channel utility.
title: Setting Up Desk Phones for Service Cloud Contact Center
